## Ignore Visual Studio temporary files, build results, and
## files generated by popular Visual Studio add-ons.

## Build results
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
out/
artifacts/

## Visual Studio
.vs/
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates
*.VC.db

## Rider
.idea/
*.sln.iml

## Visual Studio Code
.vscode/

## NuGet
*.nupkg
packages/
.nuget/

## dotnet
project.lock.json
project.fragment.lock.json
project.assets.json
*.dotCover

## User secrets
secrets.json
*.usersecrets

## Test results
TestResults/
*.trx
coverage*/
*.coverage

## Publish output
publish/

## Logs
*.log

## Database files
*.dbmdl

## Rider caches
.idea/**/workspace.xml

## ReSharper
*.ReSharper
*_ReSharper.*
*.DotSettings.user

## NCrunch
*.ncrunch*

## JetBrains Rider
.idea/

## Node
node_modules/

## OS generated files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# End of standard .gitignore for .NET/Visual Studio
